<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">The going price is only around 4000!</font>

23
00:03:16,020 --> 00:03:21,440
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">We call it Accela.</font>

24
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,990
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">It's not exactly a drug.</font>

25
00:03:23,990 --> 00:03:27,910
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">but you have to jump through the same kinds of hoops to get it.</font>

26
00:04:20,340 --> 00:04:23,340
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">I feel...</font>

27
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:25,260
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">accelerated.</font>

28
00:05:11,470 --> 00:05:16,430
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">Hurry up, come to me.</font>

29
00:05:22,150 --> 00:05:24,050
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No, that's not it.</font>

30
00:05:28,790 --> 00:05:30,780
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I don't have any mail...</font>

31
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,990
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I don't get it...</font>

32
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:39,770
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh.</font>

33
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:44,700
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I thought somebody was here.</font>

34
