<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Who?</font>

35
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:53,410
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Your imaginary friend.</font>

36
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:58,140
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Or something like that.</font>

37
00:06:04,030 --> 00:06:06,260
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You're gonna be late again.</font>

38
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:15,990
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain!</font>

39
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,200
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Good morning.</font>

40
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:24,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Good morning.</font>

41
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:27,440
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">See what I mean? It couldn't have been her.</font>

42
00:07:27,440 --> 00:07:29,910
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You think so? But...</font>

43
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:33,410
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What?</font>

44
