46
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,030
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Okay.</font>

47
00:07:45,030 --> 00:07:46,290
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">But...</font>

48
00:07:46,290 --> 00:07:47,900
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, let it go.</font>

49
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:55,100
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Have you gotten any more e-mail?</font>

50
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">E-mail?</font>

51
00:07:58,910 --> 00:08:00,500
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">From Chisa.</font>

52
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:04,550
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh, that. No, I haven't gotten any more.</font>

53
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:07,250
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You got that prank mail, too, Lain?</font>

54
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,450
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What?</font>

55
00:08:08,450 --> 00:08:09,580
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Really?</font>

56
00:08:11,420 --> 00:08:14,340
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I was just curious.</font>

57
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:16,220
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Huh?</font>

58
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:19,060
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You know, maybe she does look a little like her...</font>

59
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,790
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain, what were you doing last night?</font>

60
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:25,160
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yeah, yeah!</font>

61
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,100
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come on, I'm telling you it wasn't her!</font>

62
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:30,430
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I guess not. She doesn't look like her at all.</font>

63
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,400
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What?</font>

64
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:40,120
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">There was a girl at Cyberia last night who looked just like you, Lain.</font>

65
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Cyberia?</font>

66
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:48,120
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">We finally worked up the nerve to go there last night.</font>

67
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come on, it wasn't such a big deal.</font>

68
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:53,390
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yeah, right, you were the one who was all nervous!</font>

69
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:58,630
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh. It's a club. Young people go there at night.</font>

70
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:05,240
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">There was a girl there who looked a little like you, Lain.</font>

71
00:09:05,970 --> 00:09:08,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Last night, I...</font>

72
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:11,980
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">We know. It wasn't you.</font>

73
00:09:11,980 --> 00:09:14,350
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">We didn't get a good look at her,</font>

74
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:18,950
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">but she had on these wild clothes, and chewed people out left and right.</font>

75
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:23,150
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yeah, it was like she was your total opposite.</font>

76
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:25,950
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">But she did look like her...</font>

77
00:09:26,830 --> 00:09:30,090
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, I know! Let's take her with us next time!</font>

78
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,500
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You want to make sure, huh?</font>

79
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:35,000
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Cut it out! You're just making fun of her.</font>

80
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:41,010
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I bet when a girl like Lain goes to a club, her personality does a 180!</font>

81
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:45,780
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh. Maybe Lain would liven up a bit.</font>

82
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:48,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Right! Let's go, Lain!</font>

83
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:51,090
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">It might be fun.</font>

84
00:09:51,090 --> 00:09:55,690
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You'd have more fun if you were a little more sociable, Lain.</font>

85
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Right, Lain?</font>

86
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:03,800
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Accela, a type of smart supplement,</font>

87
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:08,790
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">uses nano-mechanisms to oscillate at a specific frequency within the body,</font>

88
00:10:09,470 --> 00:10:12,700
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">triggering the secretion of a specific hormone.</font>

89
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:18,650
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">It is said that when secreted, this hormone affects the time-sense</font>

90
00:10:18,650 --> 00:10:23,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">of the human mind, making it seem as if one's awareness is accelerated.</font>

91
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:29,390
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Not only the consciousness, but the workings of the brain itself are altered,</font>

92
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:34,390
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">multiplying the brain's operational capacity by 2 to 12 times.</font>

93
00:10:35,430 --> 00:10:41,500
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">The nano-mechanism itself is destroyed by digestive juices within 24 hours,</font>

94
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:44,400
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">but it is unknown how long its effectiveness...</font>

95
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:04,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">{\an8}Let's have fun at Cyberia tonight! From, Arisu</font>

96
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:22,010
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">{\an8}I'll pass on tonight.</font>

97
