<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Is this your place?</font>

99
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:11,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Great! I have a delivery for you.</font>

100
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:14,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'll start unloading it. Could you get the gate for me?</font>

101
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:30,280
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Could you sign this, please?</font>

102
00:13:34,010 --> 00:13:36,880
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">This thing is so cool!</font>

103
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,410
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I wish I had one of these...</font>

104
00:13:39,410 --> 00:13:40,540
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Thanks.</font>

105
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:44,080
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">All this is yours?</font>

106
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:46,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'm not sure.</font>

107
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:49,720
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Then you don't know what this is?</font>

108
00:13:52,220 --> 00:13:54,200
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">It's a top of the line Navi!</font>

109
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,890
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Fully loaded, too!</font>

110
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:59,330
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">With this kind of horsepower, you can move around freely</font>

111
00:13:59,330 --> 00:14:02,650
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">without any stress at all, even in the Wired.</font>

112
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:08,360
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I use a home-brew system, myself. It doesn't hold a candle to this.</font>

113
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:13,750
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">No, it's not like that. I don't know anything about it, either.</font>

114
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:16,700
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You will soon enough.</font>

115
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:18,580
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Have a good one.</font>

116
00:14:58,360 --> 00:15:00,870
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Your Navi came, right?</font>

117
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:05,720
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Get that mess cleaned up soon, all right? It's in the way.</font>

118
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:09,800
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'll set it up for you after dinner.</font>

119
00:15:11,310 --> 00:15:14,170
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">This Navi's good enough that I'd want to take it for a spin.</font>

120
00:15:14,710 --> 00:15:15,940
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Dad...</font>

121
00:15:17,210 --> 00:15:21,710
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I want you to set it up now.</font>

122
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:25,350
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, why are you in such a hurry?</font>

123
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:31,020
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain...</font>

124
00:15:31,990 --> 00:15:33,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I'll do it.</font>

125
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:41,330
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You can't keep using that children's Navi forever.</font>

126
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:46,340
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">For communication, you need a powerful system</font>

127
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:51,340
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">that will mature alongside your relationships with people.</font>

128
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,670
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Understand, Lain?</font>

129
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:06,680
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Come here.</font>

130
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:13,190
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Register yourself as the machine's user.</font>

131
00:16:19,710 --> 00:16:21,370
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Try talking to it.</font>

132
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:24,200
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hello, Navi.</font>

133
00:16:28,720 --> 00:16:31,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Now this Navi's yours, Lain.</font>

134
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:34,080
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You can show off to your friends now.</font>

135
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,350
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oops.</font>

136
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:44,800
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, Mika. Something wrong?</font>

137
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:56,540
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Navi, do I have mail?</font>

138
00:16:56,540 --> 00:16:58,840
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain has no mail.</font>

139
00:17:17,650 --> 00:17:21,280
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">{\an8}Lain, where are you? Everybody's waiting! You have to come!</font>

140
00:17:28,710 --> 00:17:33,960
<font face="Inkburrow" size="45">Why won't you come?</font>

141
00:17:38,690 --> 00:17:40,910
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Okay, turn left at that corner!</font>

142
00:17:41,890 --> 00:17:43,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Then go straight ahead.</font>

143
00:17:45,360 --> 00:17:46,240
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">See it?</font>

144
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,660
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yeah.</font>

145
00:17:48,660 --> 00:17:50,820
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">We're in the basement! Got it?</font>

146
00:18:01,210 --> 00:18:03,280
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey! You!</font>

147
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:04,870
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You're blocking the stairs.</font>

148
00:18:06,080 --> 00:18:07,340
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Sorry.</font>

149
00:18:07,340 --> 00:18:09,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">If you do it that way,</font>

150
00:18:09,620 --> 00:18:12,520
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">you'll get spotted by the Info-Guard Center right off the bat!</font>

151
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:14,610
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What's the big deal? I'd just be attacking it.</font>

152
00:18:15,290 --> 00:18:18,090
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey, next time we go over to that game center, let's...</font>

153
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:24,200
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What took you so long, Lain?</font>

154
00:18:25,080 --> 00:18:27,970
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You're usually in bed now, aren't you, Lain?</font>

155
00:18:29,540 --> 00:18:34,590
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain, don't you have anything better to wear out at night?</font>

156
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:41,010
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">We'll pick out something a little more grown-up for you next time, Lain.</font>

157
00:18:41,010 --> 00:18:43,620
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">You think she'd look good in grown-up clothes?</font>

158
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:44,680
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Reika!</font>

159
00:18:45,150 --> 00:18:46,450
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Hey...</font>

160
00:18:46,450 --> 00:18:47,320
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What?</font>

161
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:51,160
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">I guess the girl we saw really wasn't Lain.</font>

162
00:18:51,990 --> 00:18:54,460
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">That's what I've been telling you!</font>

163
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:58,370
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain doesn't dress like that or talk like that.</font>

164
00:18:58,370 --> 00:19:00,270
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">She doesn't look like that, either.</font>

165
00:19:00,610 --> 00:19:04,860
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Did she really look like me?</font>

166
00:19:05,370 --> 00:19:08,780
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Yeah! I was positive it was you!</font>

167
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:11,210
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Oh.</font>

168
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:18,640
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What the...?!</font>

169
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:21,040
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">He's got a gun!</font>

170
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:27,660
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Help me!</font>

171
00:19:29,730 --> 00:19:31,060
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Juri!</font>

172
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:02,380
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">Lain!</font>

173
00:20:05,130 --> 00:20:07,160
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="40">What's she doing?</font>

174
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:08,670
